<h1>Eat Da Burgers!!</h1>

<h2>Burgers awaiting devourment</h2>

<ul>
    {{#each burgers}}
        {{#unless devoured}}
            {{> burger-block devoured=false}}
        {{/unless}}
    {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Burgers in my bellay!</h2>

<ul>
    {{#each burgers}}
        {{#if devoured}}
            {{> burger-block devoured=true}}
        {{/if}}
    {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>What's next on the menu?</h2>